    "media:imagetext": "Welcome\nWe welcome you onboard our flight\nto the United States\nwith a traditional Arabic welcome of open hands\n(Ahlan Wa Sahlan)\nHors d'œuvres\nSelected Gourmet Delicacies\nSalad\nSeasonal Salad\nwith a choice or bressing\nEntree\nYour choice of:\nRoast Sirloin of Beef\nSucculent Sirloin Roasted and carved on board\nChicken Valdostana\nBreast of Chicken stuffed with Gruyere\ncheese in a nch cream sauce\nHamour Meuniere Portugese\nFillets of Hamour fried in butter and\naressed on a spicy onron ara tomato sauce\nPlats Du Jour\nFlight Fancy\nVegetables\nRice — Anna Potatoes\nGreen Beans — Buttered Baby Carrots\nInternational Cheese Service\nOn the Cheese Board a selection of\nBlue Cheese —\nGruyere - Edam - camembert\naccompanied by an array or selected tresh trutt\nDessert\nGateau — Arabic Pastries\nCoffee -\nTea — Milk — Nescafé — Fruit Juices — Soft Drinks\nSPECIAL MENU",
